{"text_id":179346,"tokens":["Our"," work"," examines"," the"," PV","LAS"," data"," through"," the"," lens"," of"," coherent"," particle"," optics","."," Motiv","ated"," by"," the"," inherent"," stochastic","ity"," of"," light","-","matter"," interaction"," in"," vacuum",","," we"," interpret"," the"," observed"," light"," polarization"," rotation"," as"," a"," manifestation"," of"," the"," vacuum"," filled"," with"," particles"," in"," a"," quantum"," state","."," Our"," approach"," bypass","es"," traditional"," ray"," optics"," and"," considers"," the"," quantum"," mechanical"," nature"," of"," light"," propagation","."," By"," explicitly"," tracking"," the"," trajectories"," of"," multiply"," scattered"," photons",","," we"," obtain"," a"," connection"," between"," the"," macroscopic"," polarization"," rotation"," and"," the"," underlying"," microscopic"," dynamics","."," We"," demonstrate"," how"," the"," interference"," patterns"," within"," the"," detector"," plane"," can"," be"," interpreted"," in"," terms"," of"," the"," quantum","-","mechanical"," creation"," and"," annihilation"," processes"," occurring"," during"," light","-","particle"," interactions","."," This"," novel"," interpretation"," sheds"," light"," on"," the"," genuine"," quantum"," nature"," of"," light"," propagation"," and"," provides"," further"," insight"," into"," the"," complex"," dynamics"," of"," vacuum","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"gemma-7b-it","label":1}